 and ketolide and certain macrolide antibiotics should generally be avoided.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/172996/', '', 'Tamoxifen, Anastrozole, Aminoglutethimide, Letrozole, Fulvestrant, Abarelix, Flutamide, Relugolix, Bicalutamide, Degarelix, Nilutamide, More', 'Dirithromycin, Lincomycin, Clindamycin', 1767369485);
